reviewText: The DVD was in good condition but then the funniness just was not up to par.
Brought as a gift.  Feedback quoted it as untrue comedy.  Three female cops against three female robbers.  No police violent shooting and fast car chasing. Just for laughs,
It's nonsense.  You will love it if you like parody police films!

Exciting! Classy! Lots of action.  Beautiful women.
Nice scenery.  If you like dull,boring movies,then don't
watch this.
If you love fast paced action with a touch of comedy,
then this is for you.
